      "5": "penthkonta agkulas poihseis th aulaia th mia kai penthkonta agkulas poihseis ek tou merous ths aulaias kata thn sumbolhn ths deuteras antiproswpoi antipiptousai allhlais eis ekasthn",
      "6": "kai poihseis krikous penthkonta crusous kai sunayeis tas aulaias eteran th etera tois krikois kai estai h skhnh mia",
      "7": "kai poihseis derreis tricinas skephn epi ths skhnhs endeka derreis poihseis autas",
